Oh, someday I'll wish upon a star
Wake up where the clouds are far behind me
Where trouble melts like lemon drops
High above the chimney tops
That's where you'll find me

Oh, somewhere over the rainbow
Way up high
And the dream that you dare to
Oh why, oh why can't I...

Ooooo oooooo ohoohohoo """

def pocet_pismen():
    """ napíše, kolikrát se zadané písmeno vyskytuje v textu písničky Somewhere over the rainbow
        (funguje i na tecky a apostrofy) """
    pismeno = input("Napiš písmeno: ")
    print("Počet písmen", pismeno, "v textu je: ", text.count(pismeno))

pocet_pismen()
